{"tid":977999,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓色情網主腦散播偷拍片判囚四年","createTime":"2019-01-11T14:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T05:48:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b94114fd3da5f20fb1b6c2fe6a95bf1ef066896","tid":977999,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:54:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190111/20588384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190111%2F20588384&d=G0inoYZgKCGyAf9ZkkeCYZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=f7a61f8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190111%2F20588384&h=5c63d864\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190111/20588384</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月11日 <br />\n<br />\n韓色情網主腦散播偷拍片判囚四年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190111/large/a2106a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190111%2Flarge%2Fa2106a.gif&h=f1b0a046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民眾曾上街示威促嚴懲南韓網站Soranet負責人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10多年間散播成千上萬偷拍及「報復性」性愛片段的南韓色情網Soranet，其中一名46歲女主腦前日被法庭裁定協助和教唆散佈淫穢物品罪名成立，判囚四年和罰款14億韓圜（962萬港元），以及接受80小時性暴力預防教育；關注團體批評判刑太輕，難以阻嚇狂徒偷拍。<br />\n<br />\n案情指宋姓女被告與丈夫及另外一對夫婦，1999年利用海外伺服器經營Soranet，至2016年被關閉時累計有逾百萬會員，法庭聲明指出宋女從網站獲得可觀利益，「嚴重損害及扭曲普世尊嚴與價值」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被斥判刑太輕<br />\n<br />\n多年來Soranet任會員上載公眾場所和廁間偷拍片段，或以分手後為報復上載的性愛影片等，導致多名受害女性羞極自殺身亡；宋女等人就透過賭博網、性交易、性玩具等網上廣告，賺取數百億韓圜收入。持南韓護照的宋女一度逃往新西蘭，南韓政府取消她的護照，迫使她去年6月回國受審。<br />\n<br />\n有份舉報和推倒Soranet的「反電子性罪行小組」創辦人朴素英批評判刑太輕，「這樣不能警告其他人不可偷拍，反令他們以為可輕易逃過罪責」。<br />\n路透社/中央社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n伊朗證實拘美退伍軍人　疑作籌碼"},{"pid":"500d519eb6572139094d144e6eb268e549da7398","tid":977999,"uid":88855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"仙人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06eb4c3b42acfd7549cd9f344ef67a2c814ed4ff","tid":977999,"uid":5205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:04:31.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"143a52d9f5494291c106a554c03ed350cc0d2c55","tid":977999,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"da849394f0d705f24a85bcef1ade15c1d676f270","tid":977999,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"trash nation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841c04d60205942b876d52ad5b1a978659fdfd09","tid":977999,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:54:23.000Z","msg":"識搵錢吖<br />\n片就男人出，樓又女人跳<br />\n錢就自己袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cdf4435871b1be8f5b8f7380e38aeca8515b27f","tid":977999,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"500d519eb6572139094d144e6eb268e549da7398","tid":977999,"uid":88855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"仙人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wvYPDSj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwvYPDSj.png&h=f959ddb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CPjgDZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CPjgDZ.png&h=e41ed2dd&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}